    "InstallUsageNotes": "IMPORTANT: DataBroadcast needs to be enabled in the 777_Options.ini File (for each Variant and Simulator)!\r\nConsult the PMDG_777_MSFS_SDK Manual in the Aircraft's Documentation\\SDK Folder.\r\n\r\nRECOMMENDED: Use the internal/GSX provided Aircraft Profiles.\r\nYou eventually need to delete the gsx.cfg File in the SimObjects\\Airplanes\\PMDG 777... Folder.\r\n\r\nNOTAMs:\r\n• The Departure Services will start when the Flightplan is imported in the UFT\r\n• The SmartButton is mapped to the MIC/INT Switch on the ACP (Captain and FO) - move to INT Position to trigger a Request",
    "PluginDefaultProfile": {
      "PluginId": "PMDG.B777",
      "ProfileMatches": [
